JPA :-
Jpa defines the Specification
It is an API
JPA -> Interface

- How do you define entities ?
- How do you map attributes ?
- Who manages the entities ?
@Entity : import jakarta.persistence.Entity;

---------------------------------------------
Other JPA implementations - Hibernate, Toplinks, etc
Hibernate :-
One of the popular Implementation of JPA.
Using 'Hibernate' directly would result in a lock into hibernate.

How to make use of Hibernate directly ?
- Making use of hibernate annotations

@Entity : import org.hibernate.annotations;
By adding hibernate jar to our classpath, we're making use of hibernate

** NOTE :- Always Recommended - To Make use of JPA.

Hierarchy :
Hibernate dependency coming into spring-boot-starter-data-jpa
JPA (jakarta.persistence-api) coming from hibernate-core:6.5.3.Final